---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <main
    class="container mx-auto px-4 py-32 min-h-[calc(100dvh-24rem)] text-center"
  >
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
      <h1
        class="text-8xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-b from-primary via-10% to-gray-100 text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-4"
      >
        404
      </h1>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-6">頁面找不到</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 whitespace-nowrap">
        抱歉，您所尋找的頁面不存在。可能是連結錯誤或頁面已經移除。
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block font-bold bg-gradient-to-b from-primary via-40% to-primary/60 text-gray-100 px-8 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out"
        >
          回到首頁
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
